<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>五百年过去了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空依然被压在山下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的身上盖了厚厚一层青苔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，如来坐在西天雷音寺中和他的弟子交谈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“东土大唐的人需要我们的帮助。”如来说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们撒谎、骗人，还偷东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们贪婪，还喜欢打架。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起了一捆卷轴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些是真经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们会教导东土的人改过自新。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那太好了！”一个弟子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们把这真经送到大唐去吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如来摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不可。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“需要真正的信徒来这里取回这些真经才可以。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人愿意去东土找一位有资格来取真经的僧人吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨站了出来：“我去吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大唐皇帝微笑着听高僧给一小群人读经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那位高僧读的是古经文。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个女子打断了高僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么读这些古经文？”她问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“难道你没听说过真经吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皇帝站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大胆！你居然打断我的......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系的。”高僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走近那个女子问：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么是真经？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那女子仔细看了下高僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真经中包含着很多道理。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>学会这些道理的人就不会再受苦了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你有真经吗？”高僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。”女子回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真经在西天的如来手中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>必须有人去雷音寺取得真经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有真正的信徒才能完成西天之旅。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从自己的袋子里拿出一件袈裟：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请穿上这个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那位高僧穿上了袈裟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>袈裟瞬间闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皇帝大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是真正的信徒。”那女子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你愿意去西天取经吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”高僧回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他低头看着那件发光的袈裟：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我的荣幸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这一路上会非常艰险。”那女子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“高山大河会拦住你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>各种猛兽、妖怪会想要杀了你，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但你不用害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会帮助你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，房间光芒四射。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那女子升上空中变了样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是观音菩萨！”有人高叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皇帝和房间里所有的人都向观音菩萨行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨升得更高，然后消失不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，宫里举行了盛宴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大唐皇帝就坐在高僧旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这一趟会给我们的国家带来很大的帮助。”皇帝说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“百姓不用再受苦，也不会再做坏事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从现在起，你就是我的御弟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们会称你为大唐圣僧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多谢陛下。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这一趟去西天要多久？”皇帝问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只需数年，我就会回来。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天下午，唐僧收拾好了行装。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把那件特别的袈裟也放进了包裹里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又把干粮放入了另一个包裹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一大群人来为他送行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝你好运，御弟。”大唐皇帝说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧骑上马，向西行去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走了一个多月，来到了一座高山前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>351259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的马沿着一条陡峭的小路慢慢走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>351260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有种不好的感觉。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>358429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不安地看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>358430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>361102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但愿这里没有妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>361103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>364753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一个声音大喊：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>364754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>369102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁在我的山上行走？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>